retz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-rejects-petition-to-nullify-ben-gvirs-appointment/0000018d-cd12-deb3-afdd-ffb289cc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列航空公司将向以色列国防军士兵赠送数千张免费机票，但附带一些注意事项</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/el-al-to-gift-thousands-of-free-plane-tickets-to-idf-soldiers-with-some-caveats/0000018d-cc97-d914-a5ad-ce97b9bc0000</link><description>该网站推出后一小时内所有可用门票都被抢购一空，数万名以色列士兵空手而归</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 17:25:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/el-al-to-gift-thousands-of-free-plane-tickets-to-idf-soldiers-with-some-caveats/0000018d-cc97-d914-a5ad-ce97b9bc0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列人拒绝内塔尼亚胡。这并不意味着他们接受左翼观点”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-02-21/ty-article-podcast/israelis-are-rejecting-netanyahu-that-doesnt-mean-they-are-embracing-left-wing-views/0000018d-cc31-d914-a5ad-ce333c600000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 16:39:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-02-21/ty-article-podcast/israelis-are-rejecting-netanyahu-that-doesnt-mean-they-are-embracing-left-wing-views/0000018d-cc31-d914-a5ad-ce333c600000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 138 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-138/0000018d-cc74-deb3-afdd-fff45f360000</link><description>以色列国防军高级律师表示，以色列国防军发现其在加沙的行为超出了犯罪门槛。 美国表示，国际法院不能在不考虑以色列安全需求的情况下命令以色列立即从巴勒斯坦领土撤军。加沙北部 ■ 据报道，40 岁妇女和 5 岁女孩在以色列国防军对黎巴嫩南部的袭击中丧生 ■ 战争结束 138 天后，您需要了解以下信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 16:35:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-138/0000018d-cc74-deb3-afdd-fff45f360000</guid></item><item><title>以色列机场管理局表示，美联航和达美航空将恢复飞往特拉维夫的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/united-delta-to-resume-flights-to-tel-aviv-israels-airport-authority-says/0000018d-cc5e-d914-a5ad-ce5ec3b90000</link><description>虽然航空公司尚未正式宣布恢复飞往以色列的航班，但美联航网站已从 3 月起提供飞往以色列的机票 ■ 美国航空公司将于 10 月初停止飞往以色列的航班</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 16:19:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/united-delta-to-resume-flights-to-tel-aviv-israels-airport-authority-says/0000018d-cc5e-d914-a5ad-ce5ec3b90000</guid></item><item><title>最新民意调查显示，大多数以色列人表示加沙不太可能取得“绝对胜利”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/most-israelis-say-absolute-victory-in-gaza-unlikely-according-to-new-poll/0000018d-cc0e-d6e9-a38d-fc1fe3ab0000</link><description>“绝对胜利”这个词是故意选择的，因为它已成为本杰明·内塔尼亚胡总理在新闻发布会和外语采访中喜欢用的词，尽管他不愿定义其实际含义</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 15:48:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/most-israelis-say-absolute-victory-in-gaza-unlikely-according-to-new-poll/0000018d-cc0e-d6e9-a38d-fc1fe3ab0000</guid></item><item><title>哈佛亲巴勒斯坦教职人员团体为分享带有反犹太主义图像的帖子而道歉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/harvard-pro-palestinian-faculty-group-apologizes-for-sharing-post-with-antisemitic-image/0000018d-cc0e-d6e9-a38d-fc1f836d0000</link><description>哈佛大学谴责了这张照片，并表示其管理委员会将从现在开始审查这些帖子。该大学写道：“我们以最强烈的措辞谴责这些帖子”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 15:31:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/harvard-pro-palestinian-faculty-group-apologizes-for-sharing-post-with-antisemitic-image/0000018d-cc0e-d6e9-a38d-fc1f836d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国称联合国最高法院不应敦促以色列立即从巴勒斯坦声称拥有主权的土地上撤军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/un-top-court-shouldnt-urge-israel-to-immediately-withdraw-from-palestinian-claimed-lands/0000018d-cbd1-dd47-adfd-dbf528560000</link><description>在国际法院就以色列占领领土举行听证会的第三天，美国代表告诉专家组不要试图“通过针对仅关注某一方行为的问题的咨询意见”来解决以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 15:05:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/un-top-court-shouldnt-urge-israel-to-immediately-withdraw-from-palestinian-claimed-lands/0000018d-cbd1-dd47-adfd-dbf528560000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军高级律师：一些士兵在加沙的行为已经“跨越了犯罪门槛”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/top-idf-lawyer-some-israeli-soldiers-have-engaged-in-criminal-behavior-during-war/0000018d-cbb5-d6e9-a38d-fbbdc0610000</link><description>在给以色列国防军指挥官的一封信中，军法署署长指出，必须对那些“跨越犯罪门槛”的士兵采取行动，例如“在行动上不合理地使用武力、抢劫、掠夺私人财产和破坏平民财产”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 14:40:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/top-idf-lawyer-some-israeli-soldiers-have-engaged-in-criminal-behavior-during-war/0000018d-cbb5-d6e9-a38d-fbbdc0610000</guid></item><item><title>撰写太空道德准则的以色列豪猪专家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/the-israeli-porcupine-expert-who-wrote-the-ethics-code-for-space/0000018d-c6d5-d234-a9ff-eeffcb3d0000</link><description>兹维·塞弗教授曾踏遍非洲森林，为内塔尼亚胡封锁的天才和才华撰写法案，与比尔·盖茨和安吉拉·默克尔交流思想，并研究伊朗人。因此，难怪他将自己的道德准则带到了联合国</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 14:05:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/the-israeli-porcupine-expert-who-wrote-the-ethics-code-for-space/0000018d-c6d5-d234-a9ff-eeffcb3d0000</guid></item><item><title>承认巴勒斯坦国是对恐怖活动的奖励吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/why-recognizing-a-palestinian-state-is-not-a-reward-for-terror/0000018d-cb0e-ddae-a18f-ffbecc420000</link><description>以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡对人类的复杂性和历史的进程一无所知，希望让世界相信巴勒斯坦国只不过是“恐怖的奖励”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 12:00:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/why-recognizing-a-palestinian-state-is-not-a-reward-for-terror/0000018d-cb0e-ddae-a18f-ffbecc420000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙北部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-northern-gaza-fighting/0000018d-cae7-ddae-a18f-ffff50f80000</link><description>21 岁的亚伯拉罕·沃瓦根上士在纳哈尔旅服役。沃加文 (Wogaven) 是内坦亚居民，身后留下父母和 11 名兄弟姐妹</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 11:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-northern-gaza-fighting/0000018d-cae7-ddae-a18f-ffff50f80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列新报告称，哈马斯 10 月 7 日期间及之后的性暴力是“系统性和蓄意的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/hamas-sexual-violence-systematic-and-deliberate-new-israeli-report-says/0000018d-cad6-d09f-a3df-eaf609c30000</link><description>以色列强奸危机中心协会发布了一份基于证词、采访和其他来源的报告，表明哈马斯的性暴力是一项“涉及系统性、有针对性的性虐待的明确行动策略”</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 11:04:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/hamas-sexual-violence-systematic-and-deliberate-new-israeli-report-says/0000018d-cad6-d09f-a3df-eaf609c30000</guid></item><item><title>无人机的黄金：大规模泄漏揭示了伊朗在俄罗斯的沙希德项目</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/gold-for-drones-massive-leak-reveals-the-iranian-shahed-project-in-russia/0000018d-bb85-dd5e-a59d-ffb729890000</link><description>文件揭示了售价 20 万美元的 Shahed 136 如何成为俄罗斯在乌克兰武库中的致命武器，以及先进型号的外观</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:51:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/gold-for-drones-massive-leak-reveals-the-iranian-shahed-project-in-russia/0000018d-bb85-dd5e-a59d-ffb729890000</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦真的“代表巴勒斯坦”吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/does-pakistan-really-stand-for-palestine/0000018d-cb11-d09f-a3df-ebb500570000</link><description>从文学节到政治神职人员，加沙战争加剧了巴基斯坦对以色列本已过度的敌意。虽然宣扬美德的进步人士和反犹太主义伊斯兰主义者在庆祝哈马斯方面找到了共同点，但他们真正在做什么来拯救巴勒斯坦人的生命？</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:42:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/does-pakistan-really-stand-for-palestine/0000018d-cb11-d09f-a3df-ebb500570000</guid></item><item><title>巴西总统用几句话抹去了他与以色列和犹太复国主义的所有热情联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/in-a-few-sentences-brazils-president-erased-all-his-warm-connections-with-israel/0000018d-caab-d7bf-a19d-eebf5c530000</link><description>作为以色列的长期朋友和支持者，卢拉总统将以色列在加沙的行动与纳粹针对犹太人的行动进行了比较，这让总统与以色列之间数十年的善意化为泡影。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:36:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/.premium/in-a-few-sentences-brazils-president-erased-all-his-warm-connections-with-israel/0000018d-caab-d7bf-a19d-eebf5c530000</guid></item><item><title>叙利亚称以色列空袭大马士革居民区，造成两人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/syria-says-israeli-strikes-hit-damascus-residential-area-killing-two/0000018d-caf0-d09f-a3df-eaf498230000</link><description>以色列尚未证实袭击事件，但叙利亚人权组织负责人表示，袭击事件与上个月在贝鲁特发生的哈马斯高级官员被暗杀事件类似</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:03:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-21/ty-article/syria-says-israeli-strikes-hit-damascus-residential-area-killing-two/0000018d-caf0-d09f-a3df-eaf498230000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷第二圣殿的奇怪石盒被发现。这是犹太洁食吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-21/ty-article/strange-stone-box-from-second-temple-jerusalem-is-revealed-was-it-kosher/0000018d-cad5-ddae-a18f-ffff2aa30000</link><description>这个盒子由石灰石制成，就像古代犹太家庭典型的石质厨具一样，盒子上有炭化痕迹——这是 2000 年前耶路撒冷被罗马人摧毁的痕迹</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 09:09:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-21/ty-article/strange-stone-box-from-second-temple-jerusalem-is-revealed-was-it-kosher/0000018d-cad5-ddae-a18f-ffff2aa30000</guid></item></channel></rss>